=Description=

"My Support Broker empowers disabled, older people and their supporters to get trained and accredited as peer brokers to help others to plan, find and manage their own care and support. This humanize the process of people find access to advice and has great potential to reduce Council’s administrative and care planning costs. They have also opened up their platform to support self funders and people who wish to plan and arrange their own care."
